{"tid":1502400,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"825 1PM 全世界入機場","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T04:24:20.000Z","uid":265019,"like":52,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"87d6c6a27b9afc17a32748a87c76f7035ea4bd72","tid":1502400,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你地<br />\n我地抗爭左三個幾月，<br />\n好明顯得兩個方向係比到政府最大壓力，<br />\n<br />\n第一，係塞爆機場。<br />\n第二，係國際戰線。<br />\n<br />\n前者導致的經濟損失，之前好多人計過數，唔洗再講；<br />\n後者，則可以發揮充分發揮香港作為國際槓桿的功能，迫使歐美向中共施壓。<br />\n<br />\n手足係前線打生打死，<br />\n用佢地的血肉長城，就係為左爭取更廣大的支持，不論是市民，定係國際輿論。<br />\n<br />\n８月１８日，數以百萬計的市民已經走上街頭，<br />\n同大家講，佢地不會割席，點解我地而家仲要綁手綁腳？！<br />\n<br />\n仆街，直接打政府春袋啦，<br />\n８月２５號，全世界入機場，<br />\n你地仲想有幾多個手足爆眼先肯入去？！"},{"pid":"0141b4e4ef1493961c801f0cbeec7d08e9b4f061","tid":1502400,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f78370c7a8974580dc98c406b51a16b6ff09b06","tid":1502400,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466dfc9cada66b84011134781af9e4a886c7345b","tid":1502400,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be413a95f294dec4200ff65059727e8f18b90368","tid":1502400,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"825 1PM 全